    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting transmission, and dependable road manners. This one shows cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections, but the core mechanicals feel capable and the chassis still has good life left in it. A great fit for someone wanting affordable transportation, a practical project, or a car to sort and drive without worrying about every scratch. If you appreciate honest used cars with functional bones and value potential, this one is worth a look.",
